The character set includes the English alphabets, numbers, special characters and unknown character. There are 70 characters in total, given below:

abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789 -,;.!?:’"/\| #$%&^*~‘+-=<>()[]{}

Each character in the tweets can be encoded using one-hot vector x i ∈ { 0 , 1 } 70 .
